1 translation units
start translation unit 1
translation-unit
  scope namespace <global>
    type A enum class A
    type B enum class B
    type-alias C enum class A
    scope enum A
      enumerator invalid enum class A 0
      enumerator other enum class A 1
    scope enum B
      enumerator invalid enum class B 0
      enumerator other enum class B 1
end translation unit
